{% set version = "4.1.2" %}

package:
  name: django
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/D/Django/Django-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b8d843714810ab88d59344507d4447be8b2cf12a49031363b6eed9f1b9b2280f

build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [py<38]
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  entry_points:
    - django-admin = django.core.management:execute_from_command_line

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - asgiref >=3.5.2,<4
    - backports.zoneinfo  # [py<39]
    - sqlparse >=0.2.2
    - python-tzdata  # [win]
